==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Mothering
<hw>Moth"er*ing</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A rural custom in England, of
visiting one's parents on Midlent Sunday, -- supposed to have been
originally visiting the mother church to make offerings at the high
altar.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Mother-in-law</ent>⟦br⟧
